{"tid":1972702,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【CEO未來世界．沈旭暉】與曾俊華對談「未來學」","createTime":"2020-04-14T16:26:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T16:26:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"984b35ffd76f0987444a0f23c5a9696934031fe4","tid":1972702,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T16:26:13.000Z","msg":"【CEO未來世界．沈旭暉】與曾俊華對談「未來學」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/r8p2sSFM3YQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fr8p2sSFM3YQ&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWVm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=59ea38be\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/r8p2sSFM3YQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n堅離地球 &middot; 沈旭暉<br />\n67.7K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n感謝新城電台授權。《CEO的未來世界》希望以「未來學」嘅角度出發，邀請唔同界別嘅嘉賓，一齊傾吓人類未來嘅可能發展。今集邀請到「前財爺」曾俊華先生，同我哋傾吓新時代嘅創業要素，大數據年代點樣求生，究竟點解仲要傳統返學等等，非常有前瞻性。<br />\n<br />\n(播出日期：2019年)<br />\n<br />\nSimon 沈旭暉 堅離地 Social Media ▶️ <br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/shensimon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshensimon&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWVm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=e4399e99\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/shensimon</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/simon.diplo...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsimon.diplo...&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWVm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=7f987b38\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/simon.diplo...</a><br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/simonshen_glos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsimonshen_glos&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWVm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=ab16d87f\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/simonshen_glos</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"https://simonshen.blog/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsimonshen.blog%2F&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWVm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=e5c640b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://simonshen.blog/</a><br />\n其他合作及查詢可以電郵至simonshen@<